  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare antibiotics versus no-treatment in kidney transplant
      recipients with asymptomatic bacteriuria.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The BiRT trial investigators would be interested to collaborate with some additional
      hospitals, particularly centers having high level of antimicrobial resistance.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
